post_title: Sleepyhead™ Bed-GS - Solid wood DIY bed with storage
post_content: Say hello to bed GS by Sleepyhead. Clean lines and pure natural wood grain in a timeless refresh to complement your bed room or guest room. Crafted with four sizable chambers, this bed frame offers high utility in terms of storage as well. The sturdy slat headboard is designed for your comfort to ean back and relax while you sit up or having your breakfast in bed.
